OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome late sunshine at first this
OL,7,Fevening then clear spells after
OL,8,Fsunset. Dry overnight with clear
OL,9,Fperiods before becoming cloudier over
OL,10,FShetland later. Light to moderate
OL,11,Feasterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA dry and settled day with
OL,14,Flight winds. It will be mostly cloudy
OL,15,Fbut some bright and sunny spells
OL,16,Fbreaking through.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
