OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure dominates bringing a dry and
OL,7,Fsettled few days with mostly light
OL,8,Fwinds. Mostly cloudy but with some
OL,9,Fbright or sunny intervals breaking
OL,10,Fthrough at times.
